Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\fad(150,150)}—2年前  西伯利亚—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哪里  哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  在流星消失之前把愿望默念三次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个愿望就会实现  是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在日本流传着的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前听你们妈妈这么说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有能变成美女的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是能长高之类的魔法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想许什么愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  星星的陨落就表示着有谁死去了  是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.80,0:00:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:01:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少在还能看到真正的星空那时  那不过是个童话罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.25,0:01:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是两年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为“TOKYO  explosion”的事件发生的那个晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑成了契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0080,,{\fad(150,150)}—2年后  中海参崴—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香烟的烟  被动吸入的比起主动吸入的含有的有害物质更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含有致癌性很高的二甲基亚硝胺  相对于主动烟中5.3-43nanogram（纳克）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被动吸烟含有680-823nanogram
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于  喹啉  则被动吸入的量是主动吸入的11倍  约含有18000纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样  想让俄罗斯人戒烟  也是不可能的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然从合理的方面来考虑  戒烟比较好这我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要没成为传闻中的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听说过吗  星星的陨落  就是契约者死亡的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在吗  那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想见见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧  是一群危险的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经受够地狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格阑荻佛龙1968
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不加水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是雪梨桶窖藏了33年的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是在这家店后面的存货中找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  您怎么会知道这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是April吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是August7？被称作魔术师的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯当局的情报泄露了  FSB的搜查是在2天后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  除了能收集到的情报以外其他的都放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,july呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.67,0:04:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经常和苏芳在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在注意你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那不是尼卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我脑袋不聪明  还总是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会好好爱护你的  我想要好好爱护你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白时刻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  该怎么办才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  我这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  可以一起回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.45,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿  那当然是从头到尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧  碰巧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  那个  照相机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才塔尼娅的表情很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是苏芳  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为尼卡是苏芳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗  别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是同一个摄影社的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会和那种粗鲁的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不是  那个  那家伙没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然稍微爱打架了点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我们高一年级  却很孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没什么品位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对小孩子却很温柔  是个不错的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅  陷入爱河了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  别说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳  塔尼娅  干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你们扫除值日哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界在一夜之间突然改变是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不懂恋爱是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我知道属于塔尼娅的那一天已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从没见过真正的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前的那天  东京和巴西突然出现了门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京的「门」被称为「地狱之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西的「门」被称为「天堂之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「门」的附近出现了未知的物质和不能理解的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就没有人再靠近那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊  虽然我可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊  这个镜头没有聚焦功能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤全被看见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿了裤袜  所以不会不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不好意思的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界发生了很大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也爆发了大规模的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这附近受到战争的影响很少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是变化也开始渐渐出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  苏芳  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  贝拉  是野猫啦  一直在盯着佩恰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  那得小心点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  博士今天也很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不能从研究所回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭我做了很多  来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  贝拉  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天塔尼娅被人告白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  被谁  被谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是尼卡啊  我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  骗人  尼卡不是你的男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  根本不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我还以为肯定是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是  啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那苏芳有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说没有啦  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「门」出现的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的星空消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们所看到的是虚假的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个天空中的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是契约者的生命本身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以理解的一种感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是因为荷尔蒙分泌所产生的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人类却依赖于此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:10:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很美妙的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得拥有梦想的你很棒  苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  把我当傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是梦总会醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像爸爸和妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  是妈妈的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来妈妈很精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说紫苑  等有机会我们去日本见妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对现在的我来说妈妈是毫无意义的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说不许在那个房间待久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  爸爸  紫苑是我弟弟  双胞胎的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是姐弟还是家人  和紫苑都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解这点的话  你会受到伤害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么  明明是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还拿着这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  她在等着我们  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳  不要再做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间只会前进  我们不可能再回到从前了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者没有心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  佩恰  你怎么想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩恰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.02,0:13:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.71,*Default,NTP,0070,0000,0070,,{\an1}第一话    黑猫不会梦到星星…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界一夜间突然改变是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见呢  你会迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅的样子很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上约好了的你也没来  为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做错了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是发现这都是无意义的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没打算生你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做这些都是毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为了这种事才告白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放手的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰塞尔诺普特放射光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契  契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者的转化没有任何征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常突然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格  行为方式都会发生明显的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会引起骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会被国家机关所收容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而周围的人关于契约者的记忆将会被抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是使用爸爸研究的那个「ME」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑  你怎么到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是在这个房子里建了很多秘密通道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我或爸爸不管哪一方遇到危险时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能很快逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价付清了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来  苏芳  到我的房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这所研究所的一切现在起将被冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都不准碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换衣服  我的衣服的话不会引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要贴身戴着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不丢掉  我们一定能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去研究所那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉知道逃跑的路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是在追我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来搜查了  现在撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  按照计划进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优先顺序为  紫苑  博士  数据
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一目标丢失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像已经逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,july  知道他的去向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  那个房间没有玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  博士的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑？还是FSB？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东洋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.35,0:18:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着面具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,April  被人窃听了  现在开始禁止使用无线电
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照C计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？  为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来提问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星核在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑吗？  紫苑在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你没用处了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有呕吐物和其他痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是MI6的April
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该已经听说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑  到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么博士死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑呢  紫苑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止  能请你跟我一起走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实点的话  我把这个分给你也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  虽说是代价  但我可不想吃这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  明天又要肌肉痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者吗  真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BK201
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚假的天空中  流星陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.49,0:24:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬的闪耀后是生命的消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤红的火焰抹去直到昨天的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧毁所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的刀刃穿透心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.50,0:24:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女独自徘徊在这冰冻的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.38,0:24:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨落的星星再无光芒  只能灰暗地腐朽溃败
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  又有星星陨落
